## **Overview**

Learn how to fold the **Origami Tornado**, a dynamic and elegant model featuring a spiral effect. This step-by-step diagram was created by Carlos Henrique Reis and is based on the original video tutorial by Kevin Hutson.

Whether you are an experienced folder or simply looking for a unique geometric model, the Origami Tornado offers a satisfying folding sequence and an impressive final result.

### About this diagram

This diagram was independently recreated from the original video tutorial by Kevin Hutson and presented as a traditional step-by-step origami diagram. The goal is to provide a printable and easy-to-follow reference for folders interested in this beautiful tornado-shaped model.

#### Based on the original video tutorial:

[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ust2zAekJ9g](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ust2zAekJ9g)

